00:01:31,472 --> 00:01:33,968
=Episode 21=

16
00:01:39,759 --> 00:01:40,320
Mr. Lin.

17
00:01:41,080 --> 00:01:43,360
Lei Yuzheng had quite a fall this time.

18
00:01:43,839 --> 00:01:46,520
It'll take a while for him
to make a comeback.

19
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:49,080
I didn't expect that.

20
00:01:49,679 --> 00:01:50,559
I…

21
00:01:50,919 --> 00:01:52,279
What didn't you expect?

22
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:56,240
Nothing.

23
00:01:57,880 --> 00:02:01,320
Mr. Lin, it's good that
Lei Yuzheng is gone now.

24
00:02:01,639 --> 00:02:03,320
Why do you still seem
to worry a lot?

25
00:02:03,600 --> 00:02:05,559
You can take this chance
to get promoted, right?

26
00:02:05,880 --> 00:02:06,839
Promoted?

27
00:02:08,800 --> 00:02:10,759
I, Lin Xiangyuan, will never
take advantage of other people.

28
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:13,839
I was gonna fight with
Lei Yuzheng face to face.

29
00:02:14,440 --> 00:02:15,520
If I win then,

30
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:17,279
it means that
I am really  more capable than him.

31
00:02:18,440 --> 00:02:20,800
But the result means everything.

32
00:02:21,119 --> 00:02:22,919
As long as you become the president of Yutian,

33
00:02:23,199 --> 00:02:25,080
no one cares about
what means you took.

34
00:02:26,240 --> 00:02:28,119
They will all look up to you.

35
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:38,800
Xieli,

36
00:02:39,759 --> 00:02:42,839
what do you think
Lei Yuzheng is doing right now?

37
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:44,199
What else can he do?

38
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:47,839
He must be crying out loud at the court.

39
00:02:48,880 --> 00:02:51,279
Now, the old is in hospital,

40
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:52,919
and the young is in jail.

41
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:56,000
Now it's time for you, Mr. Lin,
to take charge.

42
00:03:01,639 --> 00:03:03,880
Mr. Jiang, directors are waiting for you
to join the meeting.

43
00:03:06,199 --> 00:03:10,440
Look at this,
these reporters are going way too far.

44
00:03:11,240 --> 00:03:13,360
They used such title as
"Yutian's stock market scandal" and

45
00:03:13,679 --> 00:03:15,679
"Construction of Entertainment Center
project might be called off".

46
00:03:16,160 --> 00:03:17,679
They are talking nonsense.

47
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:22,039
Mr. Jiang,
that's what reporters usually do.

48
00:03:22,279 --> 00:03:23,360
As long as they can make
a big news out of something,

49
00:03:23,479 --> 00:03:25,000
they would exaggerate everything.

50
00:03:25,119 --> 00:03:26,440
Speaking of that,

51
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:28,039
not only those reporters,

52
00:03:29,039 --> 00:03:30,839
but also our employees are

53
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:31,880
talking about rumors right now.

54
00:03:32,919 --> 00:03:33,839
What do you mean?

55
00:03:35,600 --> 00:03:36,720
They are all saying that

56
00:03:37,160 --> 00:03:39,119
it will take a while for Lei Yuzheng
to make a comeback.

57
00:03:39,279 --> 00:03:40,960
And if no one takes the lead right now,

58
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:43,000
the Entertainment Center project
will be affected.

59
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,240
Mr. Jiang,

60
00:03:45,279 --> 00:03:47,359
everyone is waiting for you
to take the lead.

61
00:03:50,279 --> 00:03:51,760
But I don't know much about

62
00:03:52,640 --> 00:03:54,760
the Entertainment City project.

63
00:03:55,239 --> 00:03:56,559
If I take over right now,

64
00:03:56,920 --> 00:03:58,399
isn't it too hasty?

65
00:03:59,040 --> 00:04:00,079
I might trap myself

66
00:04:00,559 --> 00:04:03,440
later on.

67
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:06,880
By the way, Mr. Jiang,

68
00:04:07,480 --> 00:04:09,079
is Fanlv feeling better?

69
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:10,559
How's her appetite?

70
00:04:10,839 --> 00:04:12,679
I'm planning to go back to my hometown,

71
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:14,279
and bring some delicacies
for her to improve her health.

72
00:04:15,559 --> 00:04:16,679
Fanlv is fine.

73
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:19,279
Xiangyuan, you are very thoughtful.

74
00:04:22,079 --> 00:04:24,920
Ah, regarding the
Entertainment Center project,

75
00:04:25,239 --> 00:04:27,880
you know it the best
besides Lei Yuzheng.

76
00:04:29,839 --> 00:04:31,920
Come and join the meeting with me.

77
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,799
Lin, have a seat.

78
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:58,480
Regarding what happened to
Yutian recently,

79
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:00,959
I don't have to recap it.

80
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:04,000
Why don't all of you

81
00:05:04,279 --> 00:05:05,679
contribute your ideas?

82
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,279
Such a big company

83
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:10,720
needs a leader.

84
00:05:10,839 --> 00:05:13,720
Jiang, you should think of a way.

85
00:05:16,519 --> 00:05:17,600
Yuzheng is in trouble,

86
00:05:18,559 --> 00:05:20,320
and brother Ting is in the hospital.

87
00:05:20,480 --> 00:05:22,559
Everyone must be very anxious.

88
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,760
But it's still important

89
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:28,079
to maintain the order
within the company.

90
00:05:28,880 --> 00:05:30,480
Why don't we vote by raising hands

91
00:05:31,119 --> 00:05:33,920
to elect a temporary president
to take charge for now?

92
00:05:34,839 --> 00:05:35,679
How does that sound?

93
00:05:36,000 --> 00:05:37,600
As far as I'm concerned,
we can skip that step.

94
00:05:37,799 --> 00:05:39,440
The one who can take charge
is you, Mr. Jiang.

95
00:05:39,640 --> 00:05:40,720
You should take this position.

96
00:05:41,279 --> 00:05:42,000
Me?

97
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:45,119
No, no, no. How could it be me?

98
00:05:46,279 --> 00:05:47,559
Don't be modest.

99
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:50,920
The Entertainment Center project
belonged to Xinsheng in the first place.

100
00:05:51,079 --> 00:05:53,640
Although Yutian is in charge of
the development,

101
00:05:53,799 --> 00:05:55,079
you also have the responsibility.

102
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:57,239
Mr. Jiang, don't be so modest.

103
00:05:57,640 --> 00:05:58,920
Mr. Jiang, you should take it.

104
00:05:59,040 --> 00:06:00,160
Mr. Jiang, I will vote for you.

105
00:06:00,239 --> 00:06:00,679
I agree.

106
00:06:00,839 --> 00:06:01,679
Yes, I agree.

107
00:06:02,839 --> 00:06:05,040
All right. Since everyone has
such high expectation in me,

108
00:06:06,799 --> 00:06:09,160
and we should take the overall interests
of the company into account.

109
00:06:09,799 --> 00:06:13,399
I will just take this position for now,

110
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:15,920
and hope everyone could understand.

111
00:06:16,119 --> 00:06:18,000
Of course.

112
00:06:18,839 --> 00:06:23,720
But a leader cannot fight by oneself.

113
00:06:24,239 --> 00:06:26,480
It's not enough to do it all

114
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:28,119
by myself.

115
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:33,119
Lin has been my assistant
for so many years.

116
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:36,160
We've built great rapport
with each other.

117
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:37,920
Everyone here has witnessed

118
00:06:38,119 --> 00:06:40,320
his ability.

119
00:06:40,480 --> 00:06:43,079
So I suggest that I will supervise

120
00:06:43,279 --> 00:06:45,880
the Entertainment Center project,
and Lin will be in charge.

121
00:06:52,640 --> 00:06:55,959
I know that Lin is my future son-in-law,

122
00:06:56,239 --> 00:06:58,799
and I should have left him out of this,
so that people won't gossip about it.

123
00:06:59,119 --> 00:07:02,679
But to the benefit of Yutian
and the Entertainment Center project,

124
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:06,000
I think we can entrust Lin
with this task.

125
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:09,640
Lin, the investment that
you were working on

126
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,160
is still possible, right?

127
00:07:11,519 --> 00:07:13,760
I'll keep working on it.
I think it is possible for us to get it.

128
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:18,920
If Lin can collect money
for the Entertainment Center project,

129
00:07:19,119 --> 00:07:20,959
he will be the hero of Yutian.

130
00:07:21,239 --> 00:07:22,959
We can't even thank him enough.

131
00:07:28,640 --> 00:07:29,640
Everyone,

132
00:07:30,760 --> 00:07:32,279
at the very beginning,
Xinsheng cooperated with Yutian

133
00:07:32,519 --> 00:07:35,160
on the Entertainment Center project
by offering it as a gift.

134
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:37,119
Since the board has decided

135
00:07:37,519 --> 00:07:38,959
that I will take charge of this project,

136
00:07:39,119 --> 00:07:40,760
I know how much responsibility I have.

137
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:42,920
I won't let anyone down.

138
00:07:56,020 --> 00:07:58,239
(Police)

139
00:08:04,839 --> 00:08:06,599
(Jiangkan Detention Center)

140
00:08:08,039 --> 00:08:08,799
Get off the car.

141
00:08:13,199 --> 00:08:14,579
(Jiangkan Detention Center)

142
00:08:21,679 --> 00:08:23,760
According to Article 180

143
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:25,400
of the Criminal Law
of the People’s Republic of China,

144
00:08:25,719 --> 00:08:29,280
the defendant Lei Yuzheng,
the prior president of Yutian,

145
00:08:29,520 --> 00:08:31,200
is sentenced for 8 month detention
(Jiangkan Detention Center)

146
00:08:31,359 --> 00:08:32,880
due to the charge of
disclosing confidential information,

147
00:08:33,440 --> 00:08:34,760
and immediate execution is required.

148
00:08:36,860 --> 00:08:39,499
(Silence)

149
00:08:43,599 --> 00:08:44,880
Time is a one way road.

150
00:08:46,119 --> 00:08:47,559
You can only move forward
without going back.

151
00:08:48,559 --> 00:08:50,239
There's no pure luck in this world.

152
00:08:50,799 --> 00:08:53,960
Everyone needs to pay the price
for their mistakes.

153
00:08:57,520 --> 00:08:58,400
Go inside.

154
00:09:46,359 --> 00:09:47,280
My name is Liu Siyang.

155
00:09:49,280 --> 00:09:50,479
It must be the first time for you.

156
00:09:51,039 --> 00:09:52,000
I can tell that
you're not used to here yet.

157
00:09:58,359 --> 00:09:59,679
It will be better in a few days.

158
00:10:19,599 --> 00:10:20,559
Here you are.

159
00:10:22,039 --> 00:10:24,400
Xiaosu, it was on TV.

160
00:10:24,719 --> 00:10:26,440
Did Lei Yuzheng actually go to jail?

161
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:32,239
I couldn't do anything about it.

162
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:34,200
There was no evidence and

163
00:10:34,320 --> 00:10:36,320
nothing was beneficial towards him.

164
00:10:37,159 --> 00:10:38,880
He also didn't want to explain about it,

165
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:42,239
and took all the responsibilities
by himself.

166
00:10:42,640 --> 00:10:43,679
So,

167
00:10:44,919 --> 00:10:47,159
I couldn't do anything
but watching him get accused.

168
00:10:49,440 --> 00:10:50,799
It's all my fault.

169
00:10:51,280 --> 00:10:52,760
I couldn't do anything.

170
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,479
I couldn't help him.

171
00:10:56,239 --> 00:10:57,599
What happened to Lei Yuzheng this time

172
00:10:57,640 --> 00:10:59,520
is really a big issue.

173
00:11:00,000 --> 00:11:01,159
Since when...

174
00:11:06,239 --> 00:11:07,119
Siqi,

175
00:11:11,559 --> 00:11:12,719
Let's break up.

176
00:11:16,679 --> 00:11:17,679
What did you say?

177
00:11:18,440 --> 00:11:19,559
Mr. Lei went to jail,

178
00:11:21,760 --> 00:11:23,080
and the chairman is in a coma.

179
00:11:25,239 --> 00:11:26,880
It's all because of me.

180
00:11:28,479 --> 00:11:29,719
Since the past cannot be changed,

181
00:11:30,520 --> 00:11:31,799
I cannot just sit here and

182
00:11:31,919 --> 00:11:33,880
have date with you.

183
00:11:35,719 --> 00:11:38,119
He Qunfei, what is wrong with you?

184
00:11:39,159 --> 00:11:40,559
Don't regret if you say this.

185
00:11:40,760 --> 00:11:42,159
There's nothing to regret.

186
00:11:43,520 --> 00:11:45,080
Things are already this bad.

187
00:11:46,559 --> 00:11:48,479
I deserve whatever it costs.

188
00:11:49,840 --> 00:11:50,960
He Qunfei, don't be so impulsive.

189
00:11:51,039 --> 00:11:52,159
You can leave this behind.

190
00:11:53,599 --> 00:11:54,640
He Qunfei,

191
00:11:55,640 --> 00:11:56,799
you wanna break up, right?

192
00:11:58,400 --> 00:12:00,440
From now on, let's go our own ways.

193
00:12:00,599 --> 00:12:01,799
Don't you dare regret it.

194
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:02,320
Siqi.

195
00:12:02,479 --> 00:12:04,000
He Qunfei, get out of here now.

196
00:12:04,200 --> 00:12:05,359
Now.

197
00:12:05,719 --> 00:12:07,359
Siqi, calm down.

198
00:12:09,039 --> 00:12:09,960
Xiaosu.

199
00:12:10,760 --> 00:12:12,440
I really appreciate your help
this whole time.

200
00:12:13,520 --> 00:12:14,599
See you.

201
00:12:27,840 --> 00:12:29,840
What are you two doing?

202
00:13:02,880 --> 00:13:03,919
You can't fall asleep, right?

203
00:13:05,080 --> 00:13:06,880
There're only two of us

204
00:13:07,760 --> 00:13:09,039
in this 9-square meter room.

205
00:13:09,479 --> 00:13:11,159
If you keep silent like this,

206
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:13,039
it won't be long till

207
00:13:13,559 --> 00:13:14,840
we both got crazy.

208
00:13:28,719 --> 00:13:29,919
You seem to be

209
00:13:30,799 --> 00:13:32,320
someone who has power,

210
00:13:33,400 --> 00:13:35,080
and can't bear with living in jail.

211
00:13:35,919 --> 00:13:36,960
No wonder.

212
00:13:37,880 --> 00:13:39,080
Rich people,

213
00:13:50,919 --> 00:13:52,080
who's like you,

214
00:13:53,640 --> 00:13:55,880
always seem proud when nothing happens.

215
00:13:56,599 --> 00:13:58,239
As long as they get troubled,

216
00:13:58,520 --> 00:14:01,559
they would look hopeless.

217
00:14:02,159 --> 00:14:04,159
I look down on people like you.

218
00:14:05,760 --> 00:14:06,880
What did you say?

219
00:14:07,760 --> 00:14:09,239
Nothing.

220
00:14:09,479 --> 00:14:11,200
I don't have respect
for people like you.

221
00:14:11,320 --> 00:14:12,440
Why?

222
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:17,000
Too weak.

223
00:14:19,520 --> 00:14:20,559
You hit me?

224
00:14:22,080 --> 00:14:23,799
Hit me! Come, hit me!

225
00:14:25,479 --> 00:14:26,359
Hit me!

226
00:14:31,239 --> 00:14:31,799
Hit me!

227
00:14:32,559 --> 00:14:33,119
Stop it!

228
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:35,159
Do it!

229
00:14:35,719 --> 00:14:36,440
What are you doing?

230
00:14:36,599 --> 00:14:37,599
What are you doing?

231
00:14:39,000 --> 00:14:39,840
Stand aside.

232
00:14:41,799 --> 00:14:42,880
Who started first?

233
00:14:48,440 --> 00:14:49,119
Xiangyuan,

234
00:14:49,760 --> 00:14:51,159
was what Fanlv said true?

235
00:14:52,239 --> 00:14:55,159
Did He Qunfei really fight you?

236
00:14:55,919 --> 00:14:56,640
Yes.

237
00:14:57,159 --> 00:14:58,200
So, you do have something to do

238
00:14:58,640 --> 00:15:01,719
with Lei Yuzheng's trouble?

239
00:15:02,760 --> 00:15:04,919
Mr. Jiang, I've been serving you
for such a long time.

240
00:15:04,919 --> 00:15:06,400
How could you not trust me?

241
00:15:07,119 --> 00:15:08,239
How could I possibly do such

242
00:15:08,239 --> 00:15:09,640
disgraceful thing?

243
00:15:10,919 --> 00:15:11,559
Yes.

244
00:15:12,039 --> 00:15:14,000
He Qunfei fought me
because of Lei Yuzheng.

245
00:15:14,400 --> 00:15:16,119
But it was because
he cares about Lei Yuzheng so much

246
00:15:16,559 --> 00:15:17,919
that he lost his mind.

247
00:15:18,640 --> 00:15:20,840
He's been thinking of me
as Lei Yuzheng's enemy

248
00:15:21,840 --> 00:15:23,080
and always suspecting me.

249
00:15:24,880 --> 00:15:25,960
But I can understand that,

250
00:15:26,359 --> 00:15:27,880
because I was sent by Xinsheng anyway,

251
00:15:28,719 --> 00:15:30,000
and I don't have a direct relationship
with Lei Yuzheng.

252
00:15:30,159 --> 00:15:31,280
What do you mean by that?

253
00:15:32,000 --> 00:15:34,559
It was my idea to send you to Yutian

254
00:15:34,679 --> 00:15:36,200
for the Entertainment Center project.

255
00:15:37,359 --> 00:15:40,640
If He Qunfei is opinionative towards you

256
00:15:40,840 --> 00:15:42,039
just because of this,

257
00:15:42,159 --> 00:15:43,880
he's really shortsighted.

258
00:15:44,000 --> 00:15:45,559
You don't have to care about him.

259
00:15:46,000 --> 00:15:46,719
Sure.

260
00:15:47,280 --> 00:15:49,119
I will keep it in mind.

261
00:15:49,960 --> 00:15:52,599
Dad, do you think it's that simple?

262
00:15:53,440 --> 00:15:54,400
Fanlv,

263
00:15:55,599 --> 00:15:56,799
do you think I can actually do

264
00:15:56,880 --> 00:15:58,440
anything that hurts Lei Yuzheng?

265
00:15:59,359 --> 00:16:00,320
Do I seem like a cunning person

266
00:16:00,760 --> 00:16:02,119
to you?

267
00:16:04,200 --> 00:16:05,960
I've never been fussy with you.

268
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:09,080
You loved Lei Yuzheng,

