554
00:33:18,280 --> 00:33:20,239
Am I friends with you because of

555
00:33:21,239 --> 00:33:23,439
your fame or social status?

556
00:33:24,239 --> 00:33:25,079
Mr. Lei,

557
00:33:25,599 --> 00:33:28,119
Xiaosu has been really
worried about you.

558
00:33:28,959 --> 00:33:30,199
You didn't know it but

559
00:33:30,920 --> 00:33:32,800
