564
00:33:44,239 --> 00:33:46,000
Didn't you want to see me as a loser?

565
00:33:47,280 --> 00:33:49,159
Watching a person who used to be proud

566
00:33:49,360 --> 00:33:50,919
to fall to the bottom

567
00:33:51,280 --> 00:33:52,679
like me

568
00:33:53,520 --> 00:33:54,840
can satisfy your curiosity

569
00:33:54,840 --> 00:33:56,280
and compassion, right?

570
00:33:56,719 --> 00:33:58,719
I know what you are thinking.

571
00:33:59,239 --> 00:34:01,040
The once extremely arrogant Lei Yuzheng

572
00:34:02,159 --> 00:34:03,520
is no different than other people

573
00:34:03,560 --> 00:34:05,360
when he has lost everything.

574
00:34:05,760 --> 00:34:09,040
Maybe even worse than other people,

575
00:34:09,239 --> 00:34:10,479
isn't it?

576
00:34:12,360 --> 00:34:13,120
If it can make you feel better

577
00:34:13,120 --> 00:34:15,360
to see me like this,

578
00:34:16,639 --> 00:34:17,760
