579
00:34:18,479 --> 00:34:19,600
I'm listening.

580
00:34:20,360 --> 00:34:21,280
Du Xiaosu,

581
00:34:22,479 --> 00:34:23,520
save it.

582
00:34:24,120 --> 00:34:25,239
No matter it's your compassion

583
00:34:26,719 --> 00:34:27,560
or curiosity,

584
00:34:27,719 --> 00:34:29,439
