594
00:35:04,159 --> 00:35:07,399
Qunfei, you two can have a chat.

595
00:35:07,600 --> 00:35:08,639
I will be outside.

596
00:35:25,760 --> 00:35:26,719
Mr. Lei,

597
00:35:27,760 --> 00:35:29,719
